   <body>
      <context>
         <p>To duplicate a section,</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Go to Qualifications and Benefits tab of the program.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click Duplicate from the more menu beside the Section Id.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter New Start Date and New End Date.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click Add. A new section is created.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click Save.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
      <div>
         <p>The end date of the existing section is set as follows: </p>
         <p>End Date of section 1 = (New End Date - 1)</p>
         <p>For example, if you have an existing section as follows:</p>
         <p>
            <table>
               <tgroup cols="4">
                  <colspec colname="col1"/>
                  <colspec colname="col2"/>
                  <colspec colname="col3"/>
                  <colspec colname="col4"/>
                  <thead>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Section Id</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Bundle Name</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Start Date</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>End Date</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>S01</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>B01</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>01 Jan 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>31 Dec 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
         </p>
         <p>If you duplicate the section and enter New Start Date as 01 Jul 2019 and New End Date as 31 Dec 2019, the following section is created:</p>
         <p>
            <table>
               <tgroup cols="4">
                  <colspec colname="col1"/>
                  <colspec colname="col2"/>
                  <colspec colname="col3"/>
                  <colspec colname="col4"/>
                  <thead>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Section Id</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Bundle Name</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>Start Date</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>End Date</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>S01</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>B01</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>01 Jan 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>30 Jun 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry>
                           <p>S02</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>B02</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>01 Jul 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                           <p>31 Dec 2019 </p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
         </p>
         <p>You can now charge a different amount for the second section. To make changes to the bundle amount:</p>
         <ol>
            <li>Click the expand arrow beside the corresponding section.</li>
            <li>Make appropriate changes to the bundle amount or the product amount.</li>
            <li>Click<uicontrol> Save. </uicontrol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </div>
